s%20to%20Wall%20St.%2C%20There%20May%20Be%20Too%20Many%20Restaurants%20-%20The%20New%20York%20Times%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2Fbusiness%2Ftoo-many-restaurants-wall-street.html%0A%0A(via%20Instapaper)\"\\naria-label=\"Email Article\">\\nEmail\\n</a>\\n\\n\\n\\n<a class=\"menu_item tumblrShare\" id=\"shareToTumblr\" href=\"http://www.tumblr.com/share?v=3&u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2Fbusiness%2Ftoo-many-restaurants-wall-street.html&t=Thanks+to+Wall+St.%2C+There+May+Be+Too+Many+Restaurants+-+The+New+York+Times\" target=\"_blank\">\\nTumblr\\n</a>\\n\\n\\n<!-- Currently evernote share only works for save links so donot show it on texst page -->\\n\\n\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n\\n<div id=\"evernote_share_menu\" class=\"popover_menu_wrapper\">\\n<div class=\"evernote_share_menu popover_menu\">\\n<form class=\"share_to_evernote_form\" action=\"/user/share_to_evernote\" method=\"post\">\\n<input type=\\'hidden\\' name=\\'form_key\\' id=\\'form_key\\' value=\\'8fFl4vzczNmjB61pGobR\\'/>\\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"bookmark_id\" id=\"share_evernote_bookmark_id\" value=\"974806032\"/>\\n<div class=\"small_form_line group\">\\n<label for=\"share_evernote_title\">Title:</label>\\n<input type=\"text\" class=\"text\" id=\"share_evernote_title\" name=\"title\" value=\"Thanks to Wall St., There May Be Too Many Restaurants - The New York Times\" />\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"small_form_line group\">\\n<label for=\"share_evernote_tags\">Tags:</label>\\n<input type=\"text\" class=\"text\" id=\"share_evernote_tags\" name=\"tags\" placeholder=\"(optional, comma-separated, must already exist in Evernote)\"/>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"small_form_line group\">\\n<label for=\"share_evernote_notebook\">Notebook:</label>\\n<input type=\"text\" class=\"text\" id=\"share_evernote_notebook\" name=\"notebook\" placeholder=\"(optional, must already exist in Evernote)\"/>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"small_form_line group\">\\n<input type=\"submit\" id=\"share_to_evernote_submit_button\" class=\"submit\" value=\"Post to Evernote\"/>\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"cancel_box\">cancel</a>\\n</div>\\n</form>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Article Title / Metadata overlay that shows up on scroll -->\\n<aside id=\"left_context_metadata\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall left_context_metadata\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n<div class=\"metadata\">\\n<header>Thanks to Wall St., There May Be Too Many Restaurants - The New York Times</header>\\n\\n<div class=\"source\">\\n<div class=\"site_name\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/31/business/too-many-restaurants-wall-street.html\">nytimes.com</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\"site_domain\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/31/business/too-many-restaurants-wall-street.html\">NY Times</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n\\n<time class=\"meta_read_time\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n0 min\\n</time>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n</aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"swap_logo_capital\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall swap_logo_capital\">\\n<aside class=\"logo_capital\"></aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"recall_indicator\" class=\"recall_indicator\">\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall\">\\n<span class=\"ipicon ipicon-ellipsis\"></span>\\n</a>\\n</section>\\n</nav>\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"container read_content_container\">\\n<main class=\"main\" aria-label=\"Article\">\\n\\n\\n<div class=\"badge-container read-tag-container js_read_tag_container\"></div>\\n\\n<div id=\"titlebar\" class=\"titlebar\">\\n<h1>Thanks to Wall St., There May Be Too Many Restaurants - The New York Times</h1>\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/31/business/too-many-restaurants-wall-street.html\">NY Times</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Robert Gebeloff</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\n\\nOctober 31, 2017\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n\\n</div>\\n<div id=\"story\"data-id=\"974806032\" data-words=\"203\" class=\"story\">\\n<article><header><div><figure><div><img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/10/31/business/00foodglut2/00foodglut2-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75&amp;auto=webp\"></div><figcaption><span>Along Illinois Highway 59 in Aurora, Ill., several chain restaurants compete for business.</span><span><span>Credit...</span><span><span>Lyndon French for The New York Times</span></span></span></figcaption></figure></div></header><section><div><div><p>PLAINFIELD, Ill. \\xe2\\x80\\x94 The way Marcus Mooney saw it, he wasn\\xe2\\x80\\x99t just selling hot dogs \\xe2\\x80\\x94 he was selling experiences.</p><p>In addition to the classics \\xe2\\x80\\x94 a cheese dog and a chili dog \\xe2\\x80\\x94 his restaurant, Frank\\xe2\\x80\\x99s Night Out, served hot dogs topped with more exotic ingredients, like a \\xe2\\x80\\x9cSurf &amp; Turf Dog\\xe2\\x80\\x9d featuring crumbles of garlic-basted Maine lobster.</p><p>But the hot dog experiences Mr. Mooney offered were just one choice among hundreds for hungry motorists seeking a quick, inexpensive meal on this restaurant-laden stretch of Illinois Highway 59. His sales dropped. After opening his restaurant in 2013 and putting in seven-day work weeks, Mr. Mooney shuttered it last year.</p></div></div><div><div><p>\\xe2\\x80\\x9cThere becomes a point where there\\xe2\\x80\\x99s too many choices,\\xe2\\x80\\x9d Mr. Mooney said recently. \\xe2\\x80\\x9cThe more restaurants that opened up, the more it took away from business for us.\\xe2\\x80\\x9d</p></div></div><div><div><p>After a prolonged stretch of explosive growth, fueled by interest from Wall Street, experts say there are now too many fast-food, casual and other chain restaurants.</p><div><div><div><div><div><p>Thank you for your patience while we verify access.</p><p>Already a subscriber? <a href=\"https://myaccount.nytimes.com/auth/login?response_type=cookie&amp;client_id=vi&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2Fbusiness%2Ftoo-many-restaurants-wall-street.html&amp;asset=opttrunc\">Log in</a>.</p><p>Want all of The Times? <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/subscription?campaignId=89WYR&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2Fbusiness%2Ftoo-many-restaurants-wall-street.html\">Subscribe</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></article>\\n</div>\\n<footer id=\"footer\" class=\"footer\">\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/31/business/too-many-restaurants-wall-street.html\">NY Times</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Robert Gebeloff</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\n\\nOctober 31, 2017\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n</footer>\\n<!-- ### Parser\\nInstaparser\\n-->\\n</main>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Modals -->\\n<div id=\"modal_backer\" class=\"modal_backer\"></div>\\n\\n\\n<div id=\\'speedTimeRemaining\\' class=\\'speed_time_remaining container read_content_container speed_controls_ui\\'></div>\\n<div id=\\'speedRead\\' class=\\'landing_constrained container-fluid size2mode speed_read\\' data-timeSaved=\"None\"  data-remaining=\"10\"  style=\\'display:none\\'>\\n<div id=\\'speedReadProgress\\' class=\\'progress_bar speed_controls_ui\\' style=\\'top:-70px\\'></div>\\n<div id=\\'speedWordContainer\\' class=\\'single-word speed_playmode_ui visible\\'>&nbsp;</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedScrollerContainer\\' class=\\'scroller-wrapper speed_controls_ui\\' >\\n<div id=\\'speedScroller\\' class=\\'scroller\\'>\\n\\n<span id=\"speedWord-0\">Along&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-1\">Illinois&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-2\">Highway&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-3\">59&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-4\">in&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-5\">Aurora,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-6\">Ill.,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-7\">several&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-8\">chain&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-9\">restaurants&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-10\">compete&