dWord-100\">this&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-101\">restaurant-&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-102\">laden&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-103\">stretch&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-104\">of&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-105\">Illinois&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-106\">Highway&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-107\">59.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-108\">His&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-109\">sales&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-110\">dropped.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-111\">After&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-112\">opening&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-113\">his&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-114\">restaurant&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-115\">in&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-116\">2013&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-117\">and&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-118\">putting&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-119\">in&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-120\">seven-&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-121\">day&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-122\">work&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-123\">weeks,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-124\">Mr.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-125\">Mooney&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-126\">shuttered&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-127\">it&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-128\">last&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-129\">year.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-130\">\\xe2\\x80\\x9cThere&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-131\">becomes&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-132\">a&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-133\">point&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-134\">where&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-135\">there\\xe2\\x80\\x99s&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-136\">too&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-137\">many&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-138\">choices,\\xe2\\x80\\x9d&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-139\">Mr.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-140\">Mooney&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-141\">said&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-142\">recently.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-143\">\\xe2\\x80\\x9cThe&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-144\">more&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-145\">restaurants&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-146\">that&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-147\">opened&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-148\">up,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-149\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-150\">more&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-151\">it&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-152\">took&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-153\">away&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-154\">from&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-155\">business&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-156\">for&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-157\">us.\\xe2\\x80\\x9d&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-158\">After&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-159\">a&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-160\">prolonged&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-161\">stretch&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-162\">of&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-163\">explosive&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-164\">growth,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-165\">fueled&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-166\">by&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-167\">interest&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-168\">from&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-169\">Wall&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-170\">Street,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-171\">experts&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-172\">say&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-173\">there&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-174\">are&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-175\">now&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-176\">too&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-177\">many&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-178\">fast-&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-179\">food,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-180\">casual&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-181\">and&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-182\">other&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-183\">chain&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-184\">restaurants.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-185\">Thank&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-186\">you&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-187\">for&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-188\">your&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-189\">patience&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-190\">while&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-191\">we&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-192\">verify&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-193\">access.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-194\">Already&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-195\">a&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-196\">subscriber?&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-197\">Log&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-198\">in&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-199\">.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-200\">Want&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-201\">all&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-202\">of&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-203\">The&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-204\">Times?&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-205\">Subscribe&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-206\">.&nbsp;</span>\\n<span id=\"speedWord-207\">\\xe2\\x97\\x86</span>\\n\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedFadeoutLeft\\' class=\\'fade_left\\'></div>\\n<div class=\\'fade_right\\'></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedRuler\\' style=\"visibility: hidden\" class=\\'scroller\\'>\\n\\nAlong Illinois Highway 59 in Aurora, Ill., several chain restaurants compete for business. Credit... Lyndon French for The New York Times PLAINFIELD, Ill. The way Marcus Mooney saw it, he wasn\\xe2\\x80\\x99t just selling hot dogs he was selling experiences. In addition to the classics a cheese dog and a chili dog his restaurant, Frank\\xe2\\x80\\x99s Night Out, served hot dogs topped with more exotic ingredients, like a \\xe2\\x80\\x9cSurf &amp; Turf Dog\\xe2\\x80\\x9d featuring crumbles of garlic- basted Maine lobster. But the hot dog experiences Mr. Mooney offered were just one choice among hundreds for hungry motorists seeking a quick, inexpensive meal on this restaurant- laden stretch of Illinois Highway 59. His sales dropped. After opening his restaurant in 2013 and putting in seven- day work weeks, Mr. Mooney shuttered it last year. \\xe2\\x80\\x9cThere becomes a point where there\\xe2\\x80\\x99s too many choices,\\xe2\\x80\\x9d Mr. Mooney said recently. \\xe2\\x80\\x9cThe more restaurants that opened up, the more it took away from business for us.\\xe2\\x80\\x9d After a prolonged stretch of explosive growth, fueled by interest from Wall Street, experts say there are now too many fast- food, casual and other chain restaurants. Thank you for your patience while we verify access. Already a subscriber? Log in . Want all of The Times? Subscribe . \\xe2\\x97\\x86\\n\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\'wpm-container speed_controls_ui\\'>\\n<div id=\\'wpmLabel\\' class=\\'wpm-label\\'>350 words per minute</div>\\n<div class=\\'wpm-control\\'>\\n<div class=\\'wpm-icon ipicon ipicon-slower\\'></div>\\n<input type=\\'range\\' class=\\'wpm-slider\\' id=\\'wpmControl\\' min=\\'250\\' value=\\'350\\' max=\\'650\\' step=\\'10\\'>\\n<div class=\\'wpm-icon ipicon ipicon-faster\\'></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedEndState\\' class=\\'speed_endstate_ui\\' style=\\'display: none\\'>\\n<div class=\\'premium_bar\\' id=\\'speedPremiumBar\\'>\\nYou have <span id=\"speedArticlesLeft\"></span> articles left this month. Get unlimited speed reading and more with <a href=\\'/premium\\'>Instapaper Premium</a>!\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\'clearfix\\'>\\n<div class=\\'col-md-4 col-sm-4 row-same-height speed-stats \\'>\\n<div>\\n<img class=\"stats-img\" src=\"https://d2kfnvwohu0503.cloudfront.net/img/endstate_words.png?v=38f1dc56a46bae80ff5b22fe2996c54b\"><br/>\\n<span id=\"speedWordsRead\"></span> Words Read\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\'col-md-4 col-sm-4 row-same-height speed-stats\\'>\\n<div>\\n<img class=\"stats-img\" src=\"https://d2kfnvwohu0503.cloudfront.net/img/endstate_spent.png?v=324cf2e88fe14c04c9ebf3a4f354f1e2\"><br/>\\n<span id=\"speedTimeSpent\"></span> Spent\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\'col-md-4 col-sm-4 row-same-height speed-stats\\'>\\n<div>\\n<img class=\"stats-img\" src=\"https://d2kfnvwohu0503.cloudfront.net/img/endstate_time_save